tax_brackets.source: Gemini Web Search, 2025-08-10, 'New Zealand income tax rates 1969'
tax_brackets.notes: NEEDS RESEARCH. The full bracket structure is unknown. The values here are an approximation of the 1969 tax system, which merged the ordinary income tax and the Social Security Income Tax. The previous 7.5% SSIT has been incorporated into the bracket structure. The top rate of 68% is from previous years and is assumed to be the maximum rate.
